## 3️⃣ النسخة الإنجليزية (Reddit / GitHub / International Discord)

> لو حابب تنشر في مجتمعات إنجليزية

```
🕌 Looking for contributors — Salati (Prayer Reminder for Windows)

Hey everyone! 👋

I'm building an open-source Windows desktop app called **Salati** — a prayer time reminder that alerts you before each prayer by a custom number of minutes.

**The Problem:** Many people sit at their computers for hours and miss prayer times. This app runs in the background and sends you a heads-up before it's time.

**Features (v1.0):**
• Auto-fetch prayer times via Aladhan API or manual input
• Custom pre-prayer alerts per prayer (e.g., Dhuhr: 10 min before, Asr: 5 min)
• Adhan sound + popup notification
• System tray integration
• Starts with Windows
• Arabic & English support
• Local settings (JSON, no account needed)

**Tech Stack:** C# | .NET 9 | WinForms | 3-Tier Architecture | NAudio

**Looking for:**
- 1-2 C# developers (OOP basics + willingness to learn)
- Familiarity with Git is a plus

**What you'll gain:**
✅ A real-world project for your portfolio
✅ Team collaboration experience with Git
✅ API integration & clean architecture practice

If interested, comment or DM me with:
1. Your name
2. Your C# experience level
3. Which part interests you most

Let's build something meaningful together! 🚀
```

